import {
  useSettingsDeepLink,
  useAgentDialogDeepLink,
  useTasksDeepLink,
  useRelayDeepLink,
  useMeshDeepLink,
} from '@/layers/shared/model';
```

**Hooks-in-a-switch caveat (per spec §6.5):** The five `use*DeepLink` calls are unconditional (called every render in the same order), so React's rules-of-hooks are satisfied. The switch only chooses _which result_ to return.

